```plantuml
@startuml s-sokolko_smev3_adapter_service

actor Client
participant "Sanic App" as Sanic
participant "Core" as Core
participant "QueryProcessor" as QueryProc
participant "Adapter" as Adapter
participant "MongoDB" as MongoDB

Client -> Sanic: HTTP POST /schedule_query/<тип_запроса>/
Sanic -> Core: Validate Request
Core -> QueryProc: Process Query
QueryProc -> Adapter: Send SOAP Request
Adapter -> SMEV3: Send Query
SMEV3 -> Adapter: Receive Response
Adapter -> QueryProc: Process Response
QueryProc -> MongoDB: Save Data
MongoDB -> QueryProc: Confirmation
QueryProc -> Core: Return Response
Core -> Sanic: Send HTTP Response
Sanic -> Client: Query Scheduled

Client -> Sanic: HTTP GET /get_document/<тип_запроса>/<идентификатор_запроса>/
Sanic -> Core: Validate Request
Core -> MongoDB: Retrieve Document
MongoDB -> Core: Send Document
Core -> Sanic: Send HTTP Response
Sanic -> Client: Send Document

@enduml
```